<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Verify Your Email - Fifty Firsts Wellness</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #27ae60 0%, #2ecc71 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 40px 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .logo {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .tagline {
        font-size: 16px;
        opacity: 0.9;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
      }

      .verify-title {
        font-size: 24px;
        color: #2c3e50;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .verify-message {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #555;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .verification-box {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
        border: 2px solid #27ae60;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 25px;
        margin: 25px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .verification-title {
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #27ae60;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      .verify-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #27ae60 0%, #2ecc71 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 15px 30px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 25px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 20px 0;
        text-align: center;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .verify-button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      .security-info {
        background-color: #e8f5e8;
        border: 1px solid #27ae60;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        color: #155724;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .steps {
        margin: 30px 0;
      }

      .step-item {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        padding: 15px;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border-left: 4px solid #27ae60;
      }

      .step-number {
        background: #27ae60;
        color: white;
        width: 30px;
        height: 30px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-right: 15px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .step-text {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #555;
      }

      .footer {
        background-color: #2c3e50;
        color: white;
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .footer-text {
        font-size: 12px;
        opacity: 0.8;
        margin-top: 15px;
      }

      .expiry-note {
        background-color: #fff3cd;
        border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        color: #856404;
        font-size: 14px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .container {
          margin: 10px;
          border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .header,
        .content,
        .footer {
          padding: 20px;
        }

        .verify-title {
          font-size: 20px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">‚úÖ Fifty Firsts Wellness</div>
        <div class="tagline">Complete Your Registration</div>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h1 class="verify-title">
          Verify Your Email Address, <%= firstName %>! ‚úâÔ∏è
        </h1>

        <p class="verify-message">
          Welcome to Fifty Firsts Wellness! To complete your registration and
          start your wellness journey, please verify your email address by
          clicking the button below.
        </p>

        <div class="verification-box">
          <div class="verification-title">üîê Email Verification Required</div>
          <p>
            This step ensures the security of your account and helps us maintain
            a safe community.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center">
          <a href="<%= verificationUrl %>" class="verify-button">
            Verify Email Address ‚Üí
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="expiry-note">
          <strong>‚è∞ Important:</strong> This verification link will expire in
          24 hours for security reasons.
        </div>

        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step-item">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <div class="step-text">
              <strong>Click the verification button above</strong> to confirm
              your email address
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="step-item">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <div class="step-text">
              <strong>Complete your profile</strong> and set up your wellness
              preferences
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="step-item">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <div class="step-text">
              <strong>Start exploring</strong> our wellness programmes and
              community resources
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="security-info">
          <strong>üîí Security Note:</strong> If you didn't create an account
          with Fifty Firsts Wellness, please ignore this email. Your account
          security is our top priority.
        </div>

        <p
          style="
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 20px;
          "
        >
          Having trouble? Contact our support team and we'll help you get
          started on your wellness journey.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p class="footer-text">
          ¬© 2024 Fifty Firsts Wellness. All rights reserved.<br />
          Securing your wellness journey with verified accounts.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
